SNO SICEJ
MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2001-Cab(ii)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 1st September, 2001
10 Bhadrapada, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 1st
September, 2001 : -
i)
Shri Sundar Lal Patwa relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Mines.
Shri Shriram Chauhan relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Consumer Affairs, Food and Public Distribution.
iii) Shri Jaysingrao Gaikwad-Patil relinquished the charge of the office of
Minister of State in the Ministry of Mines.
Dr. Debendra Pradhan relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Agriculture.
iv)
Shri Th. Chaoba Singh relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Department of Food Processing Industries in the Ministry of
Agriculture.
